    &quot;_atType&quot; : &quot;Type1&quot;

However, it is specified as &quot;@type&quot; on model object:

    @JsonProperty(&quot;@type&quot;)
    private String _atType = null;

You will need to have &quot;@type&quot; field in json data or remove this part on model object: @JsonProperty(&quot;@type&quot;)

