The following regex works for all of the above examples:

    public static void main(String[] args)
    {
    	for (String w : &quot;camelValue&quot;.split(&quot;(?&lt;!(^|[A-Z]))(?=[A-Z])|(?&lt;!^)(?=[A-Z][a-z])&quot;)) {
    		System.out.println(w);
